<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to <%= appName %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .container { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background: #007bff; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
        .features { background: #f0f8ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .feature-item { margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; position: relative; }
        .feature-item:before { content: "âœ“"; color: #28a745; position: absolute; left: 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to <%= appName %>! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= name %>, we're excited to have you on board!</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your account has been successfully created. You can now enjoy all the features of our platform.</p>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h3>Get Started:</h3>
            <div class="feature-item">Complete your profile</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Explore our features</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Connect with other users</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Access exclusive content</div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email. Our support team is here to help!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= appName %> Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= year %> <%= appName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This email was sent to you because you registered for an account on <%= appName %>.</p>
        <p>If you didn't create this account, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>